headline: TD Cowen upgrades Despegar to 'hold' on Prosus buyout deal
summary: Investing.com -- TD Cowen upgraded Despegar.com Corp (NYSE:DESP) to "hold" from "sell" after the Latin American online travel firm agreed to be acquired by Prosus (OTC:PROSF) for $19.50 per share in cash.
